casebody.data:
No. 485. William Kinzell v. Chicago, Milwaukee & St. Paul Railway. October 21, 1918. Mr. John P. Gray and Mr. Patrick H. Loughran for petitioner. Mr. Reman H. Field and Mr. George W. Korte for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of the State of Idaho granted.
